  "content": "Prerequisite: Weapon Focus in the chosen weapon.\nBenefit: Add a +2 bonus to all attack rolls the character makes using the selected weapon.\nSpecial: A character can gain this feat multiple times. Its effects do not stack. Each time the character takes the feat it applies to a different type of weapon.",
